description:
Feed.nu API is an api that generates an android application out from a RSS feed. Enter your own strings, colors, images and settings and then generate your own custom android application. To get an api token for authentication you need to login at http://api.feed.nu/ and login with your gmail account, then copy your token and use it with this API.

This is a verry early beta version. Please contact me if you have any troubles!

for more information, visit http://feed.nu/
